		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>Wondrous Item - Legendary</em></p><p><em>This viscous, milky-white substance forms a permanent adhesive bond and must be stored in a container coated with @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-magic-items.Item.dmgOilOfSlipperi]{Oil of Slipperiness}. When found, a container holds 1d6 + 1 ounces.</em></p><p><em>A magic item like this counts as magical for overcoming effects.</em></p><p><strong>Acton</strong></p><p><strong>Apply</strong></p><ul><li><p>One ounce covers a 1-foot square surface. Applying an ounce takes a Action and takes 1 minute to set.</p></li><li><p>Once set, the bond can only be broken by @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-magic-items.Item.dmgUniversalSolv]{Universal Solvent}, @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-magic-items.Item.dmgOilOfEthereal]{Oil of Etherealness}, or a <em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.5e0swEflzMmSszQ0]{Wish}</em> spell.</p></li></ul><section class=\"secret\" id=\"foundry-secret-1\"><p><strong>Foundry Note</strong></p><p>This item includes 7 limited uses. The <strong>Determine Ounces</strong> activity can be used to determine the number of ounces equivalent to 1d6 + 1.</p><p>The <strong>Apply Glue</strong> activity allows you to select the number of ounces you're applying.</p></section>",
